# Offer Architecture

## Easy Numbers Profit System (One-Time Fee)

| Revenue Band | System Fee | Ongoing Partnership |
|---|---|---|
| $100K to $200K | $6,000 | $1,000/mo |
| $200K to $500K | $8,000 | $1,000/mo |
| $500K to $850K | $12,000 | $2,000/mo |
| $850K to $2M | $18,000 | $3,000/mo |
| $2M to $3.5M | $24,000 | $4,000/mo |
| $3.5M to $5M | $36,000 | $5,000/mo |

Client revenue determines tier. Clients do not pick their tier. $5M is the hard ceiling.

## Deliverables (Same Every Tier)

Owner-Normalized P&L Recast, Owner Pay Gap (exact $), True Breakeven, 3 Productivity Ratio Scores, Profitability Tier Assessment, Four Forces Cash Allocation, 12-Month Forecast Model, Weekly Dashboard, Priority Action Plan, Walkthrough Calls, Owner Pay Raise Roadmap, Hire and Pricing Calculators.

## 12-Month Annual Refresh

NOT included in the Profit System price. It is next year's sale. Built-in recurring revenue. Never give it away.

## Easy Numbers P&L (Free Diagnostic Tool)

Free download. Lead magnet. Given at workshops. It is NOT the Profit System. Never conflate them.

## Conversion Funnel

Cold Facebook Ads > Owner Pay Gap ScoreApp
Retarget > Profit Leak Assessment
Website > Cash Clarity Score
Results + Email Nurture > Free P&L Check > 15-Min Diagnostic Call > Close

## Guarantee

90 days. A different story. Or your money back. No questions asked. A shift, not a shortcut.
